name: MAPPA Studio Style (Chainsaw Man)
description:
Hi :D

This is a Lora trained on Chainsawman anime and AOT both from MAPPA Studio.

It produces pics similar to those animes and it doesn't have a trigger word.

Recommanded settings:

  • Weight 0.2-0.6 (0.4~).

  • Clip skip: 2-3

  • I recommand using character Loras for better results.

Please keep in mind that this is a beta version so don't expect much, but I'm trying my best to learn and figure out how Lora works (cuz i'm a beginner in Lora training) and i will keep updating it as frequently as i can :D

If you wanna support me please follow me on twitter:

https://twitter.com/xHeadshotbtw

You can also check out my Pixiv:
https://www.pixiv.net/en/users/90111017
